Currency details DZD Algeria [Algerian dinar]

Label of currency DZD is Algerian dinar.

Currency code DZD is associated to Algeria, flag is used on this site for it.

Amounts in this currency have up to 2 decimals.

It is mainly associated to country or zone Algeria.

Currency code DZD is a 3 letter normalized code according to standard ISO-4217, the 2 first letters are the code of the issuing country, third letter is the initial of the currency.

We recorded price on this currency since 1960-01-01

Current annual inflation rate for currency DZD is 4.379 %.
